snippet.title: SAINTS ROW – A Song of Ice and Dust Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Today is thine day, thy final Expansion for Saints Row hath finally arrived on these shores – A  Song of Ice and Dust. Join us as we weave a tale of marriage, betrayal and an uneasy alliance for our heroes. Set amongst the abandoned planes of the newly discovered Vallejo district in the south-west of our beloved city, quest for the sake of the Dustfaire and to protect the crown that decorates thy head.
